title: New HelpLink API is missing from IntelliSense
body:
New API was adding to Error/Warning tasks here: https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/5488, but the XSD was not updated:

https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/blob/master/src/MSBuild/MSBuild/Microsoft.Build.CommonTypes.xsd#L3219 and https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/blob/master/src/MSBuild/MSBuild/Microsoft.Build.CommonTypes.xsd#L2441.
